title: Revolution, Now!
author: Frozen_Overlord
pages:
#- We live in troubled times. The gap between the classes has become too wide. Its is time for the Prolitariat to seize the means of production and end this exploitation. I call for the workers to rize up and break their chains. All farm and mines will be
#- collectivized and redistribute to the masses. I call for the establisment of workers councils to lead this brave new world! Kulaks and the bourgeoisie should be "dealth" with swiftly and without mercy. §0
§0Alone we are weak, but together we are invincible!
#- We shall expect nothing less than liberty, and we shall defend it with our lives! Join up with your fellow Communist and anarchists fight for
your future! Workers of the world, Unite!
#- 